Package edu.uci.inf111.SelfCheckOut.Devices

Interface Summary
BaggingAreaListener The BaggingAreaListener interface must be implemented by any class which wishes to attach() to the BaggingArea to receive BaggingAreaEvents.
 

Class Summary
BaggingArea The BaggingArea class represents a wrapper for a hardware driver of the sensors in a bagging area.
BaggingAreaEvent The BaggingAreaEvent class serves to encapsulate the information associated with a change in the state of the BaggingArea, so that it can easily be passed to the BaggingAreaListeners.
PaymentCollector This class represents the payment-collecting portion of the system: the credit-card pad or cash-input part of the system.
